    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 Are you looking for a ride that\u2019s basically brand new? I\u2019m parting ways with my absolute pride and joy, and let me tell you\u2014she is flawless! This beauty has been babied since day one, kept tucked away in a garage, and honestly looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor. Not a single scratch or dent to be found! It drives like an absolute dream and still has that fresh car feel. I\u2019d love for it to go to someone who will appreciate it as much as I have. Come take a look and see for yourself\u2014you won't be disappointed!",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
