      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 7
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presented in impeccable showroom condition, this vehicle represents the zenith of automotive preservation. Every detail, from the flawless exterior luster to the pristine, untouched interior surfaces, reflects a standard of care that borders on the obsessive. Meticulously maintained and mechanically superlative, this specimen offers an unrivaled acquisition opportunity for the collector who demands absolute excellence. A rare find for those who seek the definitive example of this model.",
