    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting with my absolute pride and joy, and honestly, it\u2019s a total showstopper. This beauty has been pampered in a climate-controlled garage and looks just as stunning as the day it was first driven. It\u2019s in truly flawless shape\u2014not a single scratch or smudge to be found! It drives like an absolute dream and still has that fresh, new-car feel. If you're looking for something that\u2019s been loved and meticulously maintained, this is the one for you. Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
      "price": 46500.0,
